snippet.title: Bangladeshi Mum UK
snippet.description:
Hello Everyone! Assalamualikum! I’m a Bangladeshi mum living in the UK. 
I’m so excited to share my daily life, some cooking videos, cleaning videos, DIY projects and so much more on this channel. Please show some love by subscribing and turning on my post notifications! :)
